snippet.title: Space Invaders (1978) - 100% Longplay (No Commentary)
snippet.description:
Here I play one of the most influential game of all time. The game that invented High Scores, Multiple Lives and "Music" in a Video Game.

This is some intense game. I probably blinked only 3 times while filming this gameplay.
